Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:30.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}憎しみに　変わっていく前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:36.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}何もかもそうだろ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:41.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:50.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:55.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:02.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}壊しあって　解り合ってたことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:04.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:07.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:12.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:23.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:30.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:37.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君はつぶやいて　信じる事が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:40.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:42.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:46.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:51.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}本当の愛を知るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:30.08,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛因愛而愈加沉重 卻拒絕理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:34.56,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在愛變為恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:36.66,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}所有一切皆是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:41.71,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}窘迫的永遠是這眼前的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:44.53,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}彷彿被吞噬之物的寫實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.84,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在這被扭曲的進退兩難之時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:50.80,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使海誓山盟的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:55.15,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也漸行著冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:02.58,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}毀滅與理解之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:04.43,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}早已被遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:07.96,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}這難道是滅亡之盡頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:12.35,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}否認這一切 挺身面對之時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:18.75,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即將殞落之時 都不會逃離眼前的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:23.42,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}啊，無論如何也要找尋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:30.10,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}你的雙眸 雙手的溫存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.61,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}說什麼「愛總是只給我帶來傷害」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:37.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君之低聲細語 深信之言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:40.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}是在恐懼中哭泣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:42.43,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認識著軟弱 渴望著堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:46.24,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}當不再恐懼而滿懷信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:51.04,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}那將是真實的愛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:24.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}純真さが シンプルな力に 変わる 世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:38.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ガラスケ一スに横たわる 光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:45.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}振り上げた手 降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:54.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちるようにしゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:22:02.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:10.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:17.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:26.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:24.10,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}當純真變為單純的力量 世界由此誕生了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:38.64,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}穿透過玻璃櫥 感觸著這光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:45.74,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}舉起的手無法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:54.41,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}卻如同墜落般跌下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:22:02.73,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 拋開明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:10.22,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即便無法成為傳承的美談
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:17.55,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}如同就要失去這副身軀一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:26.72,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在極限的邊緣 跌入悲傷的深淵
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在4年前發生的阿扎帝斯坦的內亂中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同天行者組織的成員有過接觸吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:07.21,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球聯邦軍 反政府勢力監禁設施
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前也應該已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時和現在的情況不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam出現的現如今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再一次 成為了最重要的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦王國 第一皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將聯邦保安局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劃歸為獨立治安維持部隊的直轄組織
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在議會上決定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4000萬人規模的軍隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其創設成為可能 完全是依靠維塔的情報統制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能略盡微薄之力是我的光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府不能屈於一絲一毫的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了即將到來的對話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著諸位的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是此意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正是為此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才降生於這裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忠實地執行著伊奧利亞·肖漢博格的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是別人都做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的只有我們 變革者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:46.28,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1150,1008)}Innovator
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前明明一直丟在那裡不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是又怎麼心血來潮了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在那裡也有Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來 測試體E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個男的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這4年間都被拘押在這個監禁所裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個Gundam的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有受到我的腦量子波的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告裡說原因是頭部受的傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於 見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然 還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「全球」一直和你說話的阿雷魯亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字才不是什麼瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:04:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你就是瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.20,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日L1點 資源衛星群
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的戰鬥經驗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充其量乘過作業用的Walk Loader而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一個徹底的外行帶回來了麼… 剎那這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事情還有一堆的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的教官老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拿我開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾·狄蘭迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios和Cherudim的收容怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是躲在房間裡不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「並不是要回到天行者來」 一直這麼嚷著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如記錄裡所說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne和我們 是在不同的立場上進行武力介入的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說不是一夥的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:04:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也同樣用Gundam殺過人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓很多人遭遇了像我這樣的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨你們是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界原本明明是和平的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的日子本應理所當然地繼續下去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的那份和平毀掉的就是你們!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己在和平之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不想遭遇不幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉屬A-LAWS之後 有什麼不尋常的事情麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起平常也就是訓練的量多一些而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人機關的相關資料裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼人的名字叫瑪麗的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒收的所有資料我應該都過目了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 有任務了 我先掛斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 主力部隊到達了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 聯絡過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓全員各自就位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據任務計劃進入警備狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡先遣隊的皮瑞斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長翅膀那架的駕駛員…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被監禁在那個地方的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉交給上層部之後 再也沒有下來任何情報了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如Level 2的情報所述
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認機師的生存
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS也在集結起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您意下如何? 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對策這邊會開始進行 你回來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗 為什麼改了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那樣的言行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 是把另一個人格…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從王留美來的加密通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在人革領地 反政府勢力監禁設施…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…發現了阿雷魯亞!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽過的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人 是機師來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣麼 原來是被聯邦抓住了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得下落一直不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 讓全員集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開作戰會議了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 找到阿雷魯亞了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞? 誰啊 那傢伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰友 是戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼中止了Gundam的搜索!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經沒有必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部好像是已經撒下餌釣天行者組織出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是雖然要對不起地面部隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是試探對方戰力的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了阿雷魯亞是真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是王留美傳來的確定情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要開始救援作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援? 怎麼救援?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你來考慮方案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·諾莉艾卡 給我們戰術預測
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回來了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 4機的作戰就成為可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你也沒轍…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請穿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別硬塞給我這樣的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的預測什麼的 改變不了任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會讓大家暴露在危險之中而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不會後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是任務失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會把錯怪在你的頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無論是要做怎樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想把阿雷魯亞…把戰友…解救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 給我們指定戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 等一下現階段的戰力和情況的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從王留美處傳來了詳細數據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連監禁的人員和場所都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能抑止這艘空母的粒子束的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾·狄蘭迪這麼高的能力值
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:03.41,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Seravee Cherudim 發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:07.22,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機師請前往各自的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.59,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1 第2甲板……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要實戰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為你會有出場的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒真是輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內好像很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是準備幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救回戰友 救回戰友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰友?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始 作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要進行戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee 專用火箭炮裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWIN DRIVE 雖然能啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但離穩定運行還遠 別給我用TRANS-AM啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從斯米拉琪小姐那裡傳來了任務計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂搞什麼啊 這份計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大膽的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅300秒的閃電戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵… 這才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·諾莉艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 竟然連我也有分工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這樣的確比較方便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼 在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自言自語啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援拜託你咯 哈羅君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ptolemaios 進入大氣層突入程序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Seravee Cherudim 出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0043開始任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios保持射出狀態待機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從王留美處獲得的囚禁阿雷魯亞的設施中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露 和阿雷魯亞在同一設施中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN 力場最大展開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始突入大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 軌道觀察站來電
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到突入大氣層的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是運輸艦級別
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙飛船整個降落於地面…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS隊抓緊時間準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯中尉 有敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去確保E-57的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS 機庫都被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天行者的太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不減速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN 力場最大程度展開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密進入潛水模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突入海底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵…敵艦進入水中潛行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用導彈迎敵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種戰術 是為了讓粒子光束威力減半麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 提艾利亞 粒子光束的擴散時間約有300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這段時間去救出阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 3分鐘就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剩下的2分鐘去救另一個人如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個振動是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人MS出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gherudim 狙擊炮戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中也沒關係 牽制他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說哈羅 哥哥在戰鬥的時候說些什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準射擊 瞄準射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gherudim Gundam 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯 瞄準射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼粒子量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死守這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再接近一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穩如泰山!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 別的方向的攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gherudim 擊墜敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是新手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊中了 擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧 碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠…靠近不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援隊如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉去確保E-57的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！ KATARON在解救囚犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道和天行者聯手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 你為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那個坐標 Arios會來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現阿雷魯亞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 發射Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密再次潛水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GN導彈牽制 朝匯合點移動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚犯們跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是剎那他們幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是指定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了 測試體E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面在進行戰鬥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽的見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離門遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下30秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫那個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這真的是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗 瑪麗·帕法西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗·帕法西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗 瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才的畫面是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧 E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 阿雷魯亞 時間到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 明明瑪麗就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞 阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗 我一定會回來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有3架Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先確保設施的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam脫離戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退行動開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成 任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同志們的救援成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了G1的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩琳 我從參加救援部隊的成員的報告裡聽來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊員中好像有人在設施中看到了阿扎帝斯坦第一皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看到瑪麗娜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被關押了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我們沒能對她進行保護
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根據報告 瑪麗娜公主被疑似天行者的成員帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被天行者？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 提艾利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞 你怎麼被聯邦政府抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人機關的情報…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這船真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能在水中航行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛…洛克昂 你怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:22:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種反應 我已經膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.87,0:23:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一點沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有強行改變的必要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和我扯上關係 把你捲入了不相干的麻煩事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 瑪麗娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你又背負起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非此不可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 不用戰鬥的生活方式不也有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的願望只有通過戰鬥才能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣實在是 太悲傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.80,0:23:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯下過錯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能靠自身去矯正
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贖罪之旅 也是重生之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然罪依舊


